metadata.name: SmugJourney #0001
metadata.description: Smug Journey is all about embracing creativity and inclusivity. With a wide range of unique fits there's something for everyone. Smugbunny believes that everyone should feel free to be their authentic selves, and this collection celebrates individuality in all its forms. By owning one of these NFTs, you'll become a part of a community that celebrates creativity and inclusivity. Don't miss your chance to join Smugbunny on their groundbreaking journey and expand your own creativity with Smug Journey!
